description:
Do you have an intimate relationship with Jesus?

This #short clip from the message, “How Can We Have a Close Encounter With Jesus?” https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xmordFQjNkY&list=PL-k2Gb-DBYo9tb9fHW_AxGxJ1R8MpNnpa&index=23, by U.S. Senate Chaplain, Barry C. Black, explains why having a close relationship with Jesus should be our primary focus as Christians. We can strengthen our connection with Him by staying in constant communication with Him through prayer and studying His Word.

Let us have a personal encounter with Jesus Christ by asking the Holy Spirit to be in charge of our lives and lead us closer to God daily.

Watch the video to find out more about how we can have a personal encounter with Jesus.
